txt.en: Zudramdân was destroyed by a nearby siege encampment
Destroyed many supplies and weapon racks at Zudramdân.
You have destroyed many supplies and weapon racks at Zudramdân, thwarting the Orc efforts to fortify the ruins. Those in the war effort will be grateful for all that you have done here.
Supplies and weapon racks can be found in and near Zudramdân.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and weapon racks.
Supplies and weapon racks can be found in and near Zudramdân.\n\nYou should destroy supplies and weapon racks.

When conflict broke out, Zudramdân was the first hold to be lost to the Orkish forces of Gundabad. The once dwarf-held outpost has now fallen into the hands of Orc warriors. The forces at Zudramdân are sure to fortify their defences, unless something can be done to dwindle their stores.
